### Refresh admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
